                                    Dear client, Welcome to @Settings.COMPANY_NAME . Please recharge your account with mobile money to any of our packages to access 100% tips for all games across 50+ leagues around the globe.
                                </div>
                                <div class="row text-center">
                                    <div class="col" style="font-size:25px;">
                                        <img width="50" height="50" src="~/Content/coreAssets/dist/img/credit/mtn.png" />
                                        <div class="text-monospace">0785951227</div>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="col" style="font-size:25px;">
                                        <img width="50" height="50" src="~/Content/coreAssets/dist/img/credit/airtel.png" />
                                        <div class="text-monospace">0704229146</div>
                                    </div>

                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <div class="col-lg-12 col-xl-6">
                            <div class="d-flex position-relative overflow-hidden flex-column p-3 mb-3 bg-white shadow-sm rounded">
                                <div class="header-pretitle text-muted fs-11 font-weight-bold text-uppercase mb-2">Our paid subscriptions</div>
